590
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:33,640
Go. Go.

591
00:40:53,120 --> 00:40:54,720
I visit you at the deep night.

592
00:40:55,680 --> 00:40:56,880
Sorry to disturb you.

593
00:40:57,680 --> 00:40:59,360
Never mind, my lady.

594
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:00,960
This is my tavern.

595
00:41:00,960 --> 00:41:02,600
We welcome all the guests to come.

596
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:04,720
We don't mind any disturb.

597
00:41:06,600 --> 00:41:07,560
Ms. Huo.

598
00:41:08,680 --> 00:41:10,160
As I remembered,

599
00:41:11,120 --> 00:41:12,980
