615
00:41:47,200 --> 00:41:48,160
Serve the wine!

616
00:41:48,600 --> 00:41:49,520
Ms. Huo.

617
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:52,200
No need for wine.

618
00:41:55,200 --> 00:41:56,240
Your wine,

619
